	</div>

	<!-- 2 sections -->



	<div class="features-row section-bg donationcamp">
		<br><br>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-6">
					<img src="/images/campt1.png" width="500" height="400">
				</div>
				<div class="col-6">
					<h2 class="donationcamp1">Aarogya Blood Donation Camp</h2>
					<br>
					<h5 class="date">12th April 2020, Maharashtra</h5>
					<br>
					<p class="lead">As many as 920 people donated blood at a special 24-hours blood
						donation camp held in Thane city. The camps was organised to replenish blood
						banks in the city running dry owing to pandemic. A participant said that
						"donating blood is the best gift you can give someone. We feel proud that we
						are a part of this camp"</p>
					<br>
					<a href="#registeration" class="btn btn-secondary butcamp1">Register Now</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<br><br>
	</div>


	<div class="features-row section-bg donationcamp2">
		<br><br>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-6">
					<h2 class="campname">Navjivan Blood Donation Camp</h2>
					<br>
					<h5 class="campinfo">5th January 2020, Rajasthan</h5>
					<br>
					<p class="lead">The aim of the camp was to encourage the youth
						to donate blood as the region(Phaleri in Jaisalmer) suffers from a shortage of blood for
						treatment.
						As many as 568 donors donated blood at the camp. A
						donor said: "I believe that my pint of blood will help somebody to survive. I feel very
						privileged."</p>
					<br>
					<a href="#registeration" class="btn btn-secondary butcamp2">Register Now</a>
				</div>
				<div class="col-6">
					<img class="camp2" src="/images/camp2.png" width="500" height="400">
				</div>

			</div>
		</div>
		<br><br>
	</div>

	<div class="features-row section-bg donationcamp">
		<br><br>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-6">
					<img src="/images/camp3.png" width="500" height="400">
				</div>
				<div class="col-6">
					<h2 class="donationcamp1">Save Life Blood Donation Camp</h2>
					<br>
					<h5 class="date">3rd November 2020, Hyderabad</h5>
					<br>
					<p class="lead">This camp
						was conducted with an intention to help Thalassemia patients and
						cancer patients who require blood regularly. 723 donors had came forward to donate blood
						The camp manager Mr.Pranav said
						"We are very happy that our awareness programme has been successful, and more and more people
						are coming forward to donate blood."</p>
					<br>
					<a href="#registeration" class="btn btn-secondary butcamp1">Register Now</a>
				</div>
			</div>
